    "text": "Volunteer Driver Tax Appreciation Act of 2023\n\nThis bill increases the 14 cents per mile rate for the charitable use of an automobile to the standard business mileage rate (65.5 cents per mile in 2023) for automobiles transporting persons (other than the taxpayer) or property on behalf of a charitable organization."
